info.author: Michal J. Gajda
info.description:
This package contains function that allows to automatically list Ubuntu/Debian packages that would deliver a given Python module.

It may be conveniently used in sys.excepthook to list these packages whenever an ImportError exception is raised.
info.name: AutoApt
info.summary: Automatic finding of a Ubuntu/Debian package delivering a missing Python module
info.html_description:
This package contains function that allows to automatically list Ubuntu/Debian packages that would deliver a given Python module.

It may be conveniently used in sys.excepthook to list these packages whenever an ImportError exception is raised.
